folder: New Lots Avenue & Shepherd Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: New Lots Avenue - Shepherd Avenue
text:
New Lots Avenue, at the N. E. corner of Shepherd Avenue, showing the Van Brunt House, considered one of the oldest in this section of the borough. It was also known as the Hopkins
Farmhouse and the Boerum House.
About 1922
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
